'''Guinot Mary Cohr''' is a Paris-based company specializing in skin-care and beauty products.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://orogoldreviews.com/ |title=Best Beauty Products for Your Face - amazon.com |date=15 August 2014}}</ref> They are known in the tennis world for sponsoring an exhibition team-tennis event the week before the [[French Open]] from 2009 to 2012 known as the [[Masters Guinot-Mary Cohr]].

